XYDiagram.name: Komatiites (1-5% S, All Facies) Ni/Cr vs Ni/Ti (Barnes et al, 2004)
XYDiagram.Comment: Discrimination of rock type using Ni/Cr vs Ni/Ti Ratio Plot
Classification fields are based on data density percentile contours of data points from S-rich komatiite facies.
XYDiagram.Reference: Barnes, SJ, Hill, RET, Perring, CS & Dowling, SE, 2004. Lithogeochemical exploration for komatiite-associated Ni-sulfide deposits: strategies and limitations. Mineralogy and Petrology, 82, 259-293.
